game.name: Disney Princess Prom Dress Up
game.description:
The gorgeous Disney princesses Ariel, Belle and Jasmine are ready to go for the prom party together. They all are determined to look extra beautiful on the prom tonight. But, they still have not chosen the right outfits for them. Do you think that your fashion designer skills can work out here? If so, join Disney Princess Prom Dress Up game and be prepared to help the three princesses to pick up the nice outfits for their most awaited party! Your good knowledge about the fashion industry will guide them to make a quick outfit decision. 

The wardrobes of the three princesses are no short of the finest range of beautiful dresses and sparkling accessories and matching shoes. Put your designer abilities to test to design a cute outfit for each of them in this brand new dressing game for girls! We are pretty sure that your valuable advices will show them the right path towards the selection of the stunning outfits. Their unique dressing style will help them to remember this prom night always.

You will find plenty of options, including colorful and designer crops, skirts, tops, mini-skirts, skirts, a-line skirt, and more for Ariel. There will be no shortage for Belle as you can choose the dress for her amid a wide range of upper and lower dresses. You can also find out an exclusive variety of tops and mini & full-length skirts and gowns for the last princess. Make sure that you also choose the matching pair of shoes and sparkling jewelries to complete the look of each princess. Good luck to make them look attractive enough during tonight! Have a blast online, no download required!
